{
  "texts": [
    "Scripts and code written in R 4.2.2 provided in the repository https://github.com/NAMLab/DeepCRE 81.",
    "We found 385 genes that were predicted for differential gene expression, with structural variants (SVs) in their upstream or downstream 5 kbp regions, which were also detected for log-fold change in gene expression levels, according to Alonge and colleagues and containing mutated EPMs (Fisher exact test statistic value is <0.00001).",
    "Six genes from the fifteen genotypes were randomly selected for in-detail analyses aligned with MAFFT 82 (Supplementary Data 8, 9).",
    "EPMs extracted from the leaf MSR model of S. lycopersicum were mapped to the candidate gene alignments with BLAMM 37 (Supplementary Data 8).",
    "Up-and downstream gene regions were investigated manually for the presence of structural variants and other mutations within regions matching EPMs in their positional preferred ranges and annotated (Supplementary Data 9)."
  ]
}